You can start using the fonts by following these instructions:

Add the following line to the "Files" section of your X.Org
configuration file:

	FontPath "%%FONTSDIR%%/"

Please also note that this font will only look good if used at the
following sizes:

        12 px or 9 pt
        14 px or 10.5 pt
        16 px or 12 pt
        18 px or 13.5 pt
        20 px or 15 pt
        22 px or 16.5 pt
        24 px or 18 pt
        28 px or 21 pt
        32 px or 24 pt
